{"rendered": {"description": {"raw": "This PR, together with the [PR](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/pull-requests/184), add Actor support in skeleton. Basically, it add following function to support Actor animation:\r\n\r\n* `AddBvhAnimation`: load bvh animation for the skeleton\r\n* `AlignTranslation`: translation alignment \\(node local transformations\\) from the animation skeleton to mesh skeleton\r\n* `AlignRotation`: rotation alignment \\(node local transformations\\) from the animation skeleton to mesh skeleton\r\n* `NodeNameAnimToSkin`: node name mapping from animation skeleton to mesh skeleton\r\n\r\nAlso, a new class `TrajectoryInfo` is created in `Animation` class for actor trajectory.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>This PR, together with the <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/pull-requests/184\" rel=\"nofollow\">PR</a>, add Actor support in skeleton. Basically, it add following function to support Actor animation:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>AddBvhAnimation</code>: load bvh animation for the skeleton</li>\n<li><code>AlignTranslation</code>: translation alignment (node local transformations) from the animation skeleton to mesh skeleton</li>\n<li><code>AlignRotation</code>: rotation alignment (node local transformations) from the animation skeleton to mesh skeleton</li>\n<li><code>NodeNameAnimToSkin</code>: node name mapping from animation skeleton to mesh skeleton</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, a new class <code>TrajectoryInfo</code> is created in <code>Animation</code> class for actor trajectory.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "title": {"raw": "add bvh animation support for skeleton", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>add bvh animation support for skeleton</p>", "type": "rendered"}}, "type": "pullrequest", "description": "This PR, together with the [PR](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/pull-requests/184), add Actor support in skeleton. Basically, it add following function to support Actor animation:\r\n\r\n* `AddBvhAnimation