 skeleton to mesh skeleton</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, a new class <code>TrajectoryInfo</code> is created in <code>Animation</code> class for actor trajectory.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "source": {"commit": {"hash": "14a1dd283613", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/mingfeisun/ign-common/commit/14a1dd283613"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/mingfeisun/ign-common/commits/14a1dd283613"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/mingfeisun/ign-common"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/mingfeisun/ign-common"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{f325c82c-154a-4471-81c9-be4bf87a29b0}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-common", "full_name": "mingfeisun/ign-common", "uuid": "{f325c82c-154a-4471-81c9-be4bf87a29b0}"}, "branch": {"name": "ign-common3"}}, "comment_count": 45, "state": "MERGED", "task_count": 0, "participants": [{"role": "PARTICIPANT", "participated_on": "2019-08-17T05:34:31.285399+00:00", "type": "participant", "approved": false, "user": {"display_name": "mingfei sun", "uuid": "{1e5a944b-56e4-4808-b81d-d6de318feadc}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B1e5a944b-56e4-4808-b81d-d6de318feadc%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B1e5a944b-56e4-4808-b81d-d6de318feadc%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a4be22d43d004c04e5f8fee72a65d214d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsMS-1.png"}}, "nickname": "mingfeisun", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:ad32c2b0-bebb-403e-b385-c3c1f7aa1d09"}}, {"role": "PARTICIPANT", "participated_on": "2019-07-27T00:05:57.255436+00:00", "type": "participant", "approved": false, "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "h